    "Gong and Zhang (2023) 8.",
    "Images collected from the field -A method of re-parameterization was presented to improve the boosting accuracy of convolutional neural networks.",
    "A dynamic pruning gate was used to regulate the network structure dynamically.",
    "Subclasses with low detection accuracy were improved by data augmentation and verified by ablation tests for model correctness.",
    "Finally, the model was 0.94 accurate."
